{"tid":638343,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（孝子）有咩岩老人家做既運動","createTime":"2018-04-22T15:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T10:23:55.000Z","uid":177630,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d8aa520f5222b69847bcab06bf825c63b415125c","tid":638343,"uid":177630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T15:35:08.000Z","msg":"我老豆就一把年紀成七十歲，又有多年糖尿病（比起好多人黎講控制得幾好，唔洗胰島素），同埋今年開始左肩痛到郁唔到咁濟，搞到佢愈黎愈唔肯做運動。<br />\n<br />\n佢平時最鍾意出街急步行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但講真咁樣冇乜用，見佢食野又唔肯食多d(驚血糖），而家又話隻手痛到郁唔到，見到佢d肌肉愈黎愈少就好撚擔心。老人家咁樣適合做咩運動呢？佢又唔肯太極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw窮撚睇政府physio覺得好無力，一時話佢肩周炎一時話五十肩，有冇巴絲知可以點樣check到問題係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝各巴絲父母健健康康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cdbb9a5090f552ad4d0b628b795d483a09b0f1f","tid":638343,"uid":132219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"同問 我媽63歲都係好少做運動 依家連行樓梯都喘晒氣 對腳又冇乜力<br />\n<br />\n只求佢身體健康 享到仔福女福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacbe26765f8df7ccb3614736174809dda853812","tid":638343,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"太極 練氣功"},{"pid":"b8447f8f75f5d8e5cdcc8162a96273557154a45f","tid":638343,"uid":51134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:29:58.000Z","msg":"日日行路 (20分鐘以上)<br />\n<br />\n強度大概係 要同人講到嘢 唔會索曬氣"},{"pid":"f6dc5040c48a6a94b5283acd58a8cba33d11029d","tid":638343,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4c600e9e4e9b7575bef2e59fac9ba9572b5b9bf","tid":638343,"uid":14496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"肩周炎=五十肩"},{"pid":"822ca5b96d0d349cfbdf91c24971dd0d653b7211","tid":638343,"uid":1316